[lodash groupBy][1] returns an `Object` not an `Array` therefore the javascript .map call will not work on it. Also groupBy is used to group items with similar property under one key inside an object, it isn&#39;t used to remove duplicates.

To remove duplicates use the [lodash uniqBy][2] method. This method can be called on an array and returns an array without duplicates.

